reviewText: Amazing instruction from an amazing instructor.
straight to the point and simplistic to learn...

A MUST HAVE for anyone serious about being in battle-ready shape with their rifle. Outstanding briefing, drill set up, execution, and debriefing. This is what separates the real life warriors from the competitive shooters.
Looking forward to working on thses drills and matching the time, also brings a new dynamic, with physical stressor and gun manipulation. Great stuff.
